rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0001
rows.name:
E-Emperor Hugo?! Your Majesty!
My apologies for not
recognizing you before...

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I must say that this Superbian-made
ship is quite remarkable.

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We have Divine Beast ships
in Gula too, but nothing
quite as impressive as this!

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, it's clear that we
need to build a friendly
relationship with Superbia.

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But actually, there are still those
among the Gulan elders who do not
take kindly to Superbians.

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0006
rows.name:
If the truth be known, one of the
aims of this conference was to find
out the best persuasive arguments.

rows.label: tlk70000089_01_msg0007
rows.name:
But at the very least, I promise to
advise the elders that you, sir, and
your friends are worthy of our trust.
